---
title: Mumbai Crumbed Pork with Spiced Roast Veggie Toss & Yoghurt
description: A crumbed pork schnitzel is a classic that we’ll never get tired of - but who’s in for a flavour twist? We are! Let’s throw warm Mumbai spices right into the crumb, and serve it alongside spiced roast veggies and cooling yoghurt. Yum!
